syslog(3) for Haskell_
======================

:Latest Release: syslog-2004-10-14.tar.gz_
:Darcs:          darcs_ get --partial http://cryp.to/syslog/

Synopsis
--------

  The ``Syslog.hs`` modules provides FFI bindings to
  ``syslog(3)``. The bindings are somewhat incomplete; right
  now there is no way to set log-masks, for example. Patches
  are highly welcome. Process the file with ``hsc2hs`` to
  obtain a plain Haskell module.

Documentation
-------------

  `Reference Documentation`_
     Haddock-generated reference of all exported
     functions.

